# Vincent — architecture

Kotlin Multiplatform wine cellar app. **UI in `commonMain`**, Android-only target wired.
Package: `fr.geoking.vincent`. Full docs: `README.md`.

## Before exploring

1. Read `README.md` (Architecture, Wine data providers, Notes) for the answer.
2. Open the **specific file** listed below — do not scan the whole tree.
3. Only grep/read broadly when the question spans multiple subsystems.

## Key files

| Concern | File |
|---------|------|
| Root nav + bottom tabs | `composeApp/src/commonMain/.../App.kt` |
| Back gesture | `Navigation.kt` (expect/actual) |
| In-memory state (SSOT) | `data/Cellar.kt` |
| Domain models | `model/Models.kt`, `model/SampleData.kt` |
| Persistence seam | `data/CellarRepository.kt` → `androidMain/.../db/RoomCellarRepository.kt` |
| Android bootstrap | `androidMain/.../MainActivity.kt` (Room + auth + updates) |
| Theme (lie-de-vin) | `theme/Theme.kt` |
| Shared UI widgets | `ui/` (`WineBottle`, `Components.kt`, …) |
| Feature flags | `FeatureFlags.kt` |
| Cloud sync | `data/CloudSync.kt` + `CloudSync.android.kt` |
| Firebase rules | `firestore.rules` (project `vincent-499318`) |
| CI / release | `.github/workflows/`, `scripts/setup-release.sh` |
| Landing page | `website/` (Cloudflare Pages) |
| AI proxy worker | `worker/` |

## Stack

Kotlin 2.3 · Compose MP 1.11 · Material 3 · Room (KSP) · JDK 21 · min SDK 24.

## Conventions

- Mutate cellar via `Cellar` API (`addBottle`, `adjustQuantity`, `toggleFavorite`) — screens stay reactive.
- Platform code: `expect` in `commonMain`, `actual` in `androidMain`.
- Secrets via `secret()` in `composeApp/build.gradle.kts` → `local.properties` (gitignored).
- `local.properties` must never be committed.
